crosoft\u00ae Xbox\u00ae One Elite Controller<br>SONY\u00ae PS4 DUALSHOCK\u00ae4 wireless controller (Wired)<br>Logitech RumblePad\u2122 2<br>Logitech\u2122 Dual Action\u2122<br>Logitech\u2122 Wireless Gamepad F710<br>Logitech\u2122 Gamepad F310<br>Afterglow Wired Controller for Xbox 360<br>Rock Candy Controller for Xbox 360<br>Thrustmaster GPX Controller for Xbox 360<br>RAZER Sabertooth",
